<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>SEAS Document Scanning Guide</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 40px; color: #333; line-height: 1.5; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; border-bottom: 2px solid #046d40; padding-bottom: 16px; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #00193c; font-size: 26px; }
    .section { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #00193c; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; }
    li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .tip { background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #046d40; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 12px; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px; }
    th, td { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; }
    th { background: #f8fafc; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Document Scanning Guide</h1>
    <p>SEAS Candidate Portal · Document Center</p>
    <p>Generated: {{generatedAt}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Accepted File Formats</div>
    <ul>
      <li>PDF (preferred for multi-page documents)</li>
      <li>JPEG or PNG images (minimum 300 DPI recommended)</li>
      <li>Maximum file size: 10 MB per upload</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Required Documents</div>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Document</th><th>Requirements</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>National ID / Passport</td><td>Full page, all corners visible, no glare</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Academic Transcripts</td><td>All semesters legible; official stamp if available</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Degrees &amp; Diplomas</td><td>Official certificate or provisional completion letter</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Passport Photo</td><td>Plain background, face clearly visible</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Scanning Best Practices</div>
    <ul>
      <li>Use a flat surface and even lighting; avoid shadows across text.</li>
      <li>Ensure all four corners of the document are visible in the scan.</li>
      <li>Do not crop off seals, signatures, or page numbers.</li>
      <li>For phone scans, use a document-scanning app with edge detection.</li>
      <li>Name files clearly before upload (e.g. <em>transcript-2024.pdf</em>).</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="tip">
      <strong>Tip:</strong> Blurry or incomplete uploads may delay verification. Re-upload before your application deadline if rejected.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Need Help?</div>
    <p style="font-size: 13px;">Contact the registrar at admissions@seas.cm if you cannot obtain an official copy before the deadline.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
